rows.label: qst201911_msg0001
rows.name:
Where is it?! Where's the money?!
Speak or suffer the consequences!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0002
rows.name: W-what going on?! What money?

rows.label: qst201911_msg0003
rows.name:
The money inside the barrels!
That is what's going on!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0004
rows.name:
The money you robbed us of was
supposed to be in the four buried
barrels, but it wasn't! Where is it?!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0005
rows.name: N-not know what you talking about...

rows.label: qst201911_msg0006
rows.name:
Do not play dumb with us!
We know it was you!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0007
rows.name: You rotten, black-feathered wretch!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0008
rows.name:
How long do you plan to string
us along?!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0009
rows.name:
Spit it out. Or we will make it so that
you speak no more!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0010
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh-meeeeeeh!!!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0011
rows.name: Please, forgive us!!!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0012
rows.name: We not know anything, really!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0013
rows.name:
Only leader know what inside barrels!
We just do as we told...

rows.label: qst201911_msg0014
rows.name:
And where, then, is this leader of
yours, mmm?

rows.label: qst201911_msg0015
rows.name:
Where is he?! Lay him before us this
instant!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0016
rows.name:
L-leader is Suisui! You already kick him
into middle of next week!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0017
rows.name:
Suisui go flying... Is mystery where he
went after that...

rows.label: qst201911_msg0019
rows.name:
Ah, err... We see. That does put
a damper on the issue.

rows.label: qst201911_msg0020
rows.name:
Get yourselves ready, all! We shall
commence a search for Suisui at once!

rows.label: qst201911_msg0021
rows.name:
I don't think we should just run around
like headless Tirkin, though...

rows.label: qst201911_msg0022
rows.name: Then what would you suggest?

rows.label: qst201911_msg0023
rows.name:
Well, how about we get the mercs
to help us out?

rows.label: qst201911_msg0024
rows.name:
I'm sure they'll be much faster sniffing
out the guy than us.
